ActYukon Placer Mining Act
Yukon Quartz Mining Act
PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (2002, No. 11, VUNTUT GWITCHIN FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits, until February 1, 2008, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on lands in the Yukon, and (b) repeals the Prohibition of Entry Order made in 1998.
